content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1220.77 - Unclaimed parcels subject to sale 11 months from date checked

State Regulations

Parcels will be held by the Port Authority for a period
of 11 months after checking. Unclaimed parcels remaining after 11 months may be
sold at public or private sale to satisfy accrued charges. Notes
